The use of consistency regularization and pseudo-labeling also suggests that it may fall under the subcategories of natural language processing (cs.CL) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper uses deep neural networks, which suggests that it may fall under the subcategory of neural networks (cs.NE).
